OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FTwo men charged with the murder of
OL,7,FNicholas Gordon in east Belfast
OL,8,Fallegedly "gloated" about what they
OL,9,Fhad done after assaulting him, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FThe 51-year-old, who is known as
OL,13,FNicky, died in hospital from his
OL,14,Finjuries after being allegedly
OL,15,Fattacked by the pair using a brush
OL,16,Fshaft at an apartment complex on the
OL,17,FHolywood Road in the early hours of
OL,18,FMay 12.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
