PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FPolice said they found him conscious
OL,7,Fbut badly injured, and he died several
OL,8,Fdays later in the Royal Victoria
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FChristopher Colin Nobes, 31, of no
OL,12,Ffixed abode, and Andrew John Matthews,
OL,13,F25, also of no fixed abode, have both
OL,14,Fbeen charged with murdering Mr Gordon
OL,15,Fon May 15, as well as a number of
OL,16,Fother offences.
OL,18,FThey were both remanded in custody
OL,19,Ffollowing the brief first appearance
OL,20,Fat Belfast Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FFriday morning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
