CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FNobes has also been charged with
OL,7,Fmaking threats to kill two named women
OL,8,Fon May 12, theft of a phone and a bank
OL,9,Fcard from Mr Gordon on May 12, as well
OL,10,Fas aggravated burglary with intent to
OL,11,Finflict grievous bodily harm on Mr
OL,12,FGordon with a brush shaft.
OL,14,FHe is also charged with possession of
OL,15,Fa BB gun on May 11.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
