OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FMatthews is charged with making
OL,7,Fthreats to kill two named women,
OL,8,Faggravated burglary with intent to
OL,9,Finflict grievous bodily harm on Mr
OL,10,FGordon with a brush shaft, theft of a
OL,11,Fmobile phone and bank card from Mr
OL,12,FGordon on May 12, and criminal damage
OL,13,Fof a TV belonging to Mr Gordon on May
OL,14,F12.
OL,16,FHe is also charged with possession of
OL,17,Fa BB gun on May 11.
OL,19,FA detective inspector told the court
OL,20,Fshe believes police can connect the
OL,21,Faccused to the charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
