PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FShe described a "number of incidents"
OL,7,Fwhich started at around 10.30pm on
OL,8,FSunday May 10 in the Shorts Social
OL,9,FClub in east Belfast.
OL,11,F"It is alleged that both Nobes and
OL,12,FMatthews were causing some anti-social
OL,13,Fbehaviour resulting in a banning order
OL,14,Fbeing issued by the manager there at
OL,15,Fthe social club," she told the court.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@eO]sD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FShe went on to say that Nobes and
OL,7,FMatthews are alleged to have been
OL,8,Finvolved in an assault involving three
OL,9,Fforeign nationals at around 8.52pm on
OL,10,FMay 11 at Tesco in Knocknagoney,
OL,11,Ffootage of which, she said, was
OL,12,F"widely viewed on social media".
OL,14,FThe detective inspector said Nobes and
OL,15,FMatthews were at the apartment complex
OL,16,Fon the Holywood Road in the early
OL,17,Fhours of Tuesday May 12.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,F"Nobes and Matthews attended that
OL,7,Fapartment block and assaulted Nicky
OL,8,FGordon in his apartment at flat 16,
OL,9,Fpolice received a report of that
OL,10,Fassault at 8.24am on Tuesday May 12,
OL,11,Fwhen police attended they found Nicky
OL,12,FGordon who was conscious but very
OL,13,Fbadly beaten," she said.
OL,15,F"He was taken to the Royal Victoria
OL,16,FHospital where he died."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@NO]wD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
