CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FShe said police have established the
OL,7,Fpair arrived at the apartment complex
OL,8,Fat around 3am and first stayed in a
OL,9,Fdifferent flat with a number of
OL,10,Fwitnesses, before going upstairs to Mr
OL,11,FGordon's flat around 4.45am.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,F"They forcibly entered flat 16 on
OL,7,Fthree occasions and assaulted Nicky
OL,8,FGordon with what is alleged to be a
OL,9,Fbrush shaft, they came back down to
OL,10,Fthe apartment they had been staying in
OL,11,Fand a number of witnesses stated they
OL,12,Fwere gloating about what they had
OL,13,Fdone, and also about the previous
OL,14,Fincidents at Shorts Social Club and at
OL,15,FTesco."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
