OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,FShe said the pair also allegedly
OL,7,Fdamaged a television in Mr Gordon's
OL,8,Fflat by "taking it off the wall and
OL,9,Fthrowing it out the window", and
OL,10,Fthreatened a number of witnesses that
OL,11,Fthey would be shot if they reported
OL,12,Fthe matter to police.
OL,14,FThe detective inspector said the
OL,15,Fdefendants then left Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fon Wednesday May 13 to travel to
OL,17,FScotland "under false names", where
OL,18,Fthey were later apprehended by Police
OL,19,FScotland and returned to Northern
OL,20,FIreland.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@[O]yD@JOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779718268
OL,3,CPolice believe Belfast man was
OL,4,Cattacked with brush shaft before death
OL,6,F"The evidence against them is witness
OL,7,Fstatements, CCTV and there is a
OL,8,Ffingerprint of Christopher Nobes on
OL,9,Fthe exterior doorframe of the flat
OL,10,Fbelonging to Nicky Gordon," she added.
OL,12,FA solicitor for Nobes said his client
OL,13,F"vehemently denies the allegations".
OL,15,FNo application for bail was made.
OL,17,FBoth men were remanded in custody to
OL,18,Fappear next on June 19.
